{"tid":1453317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家今日喺機場除左叫口號仲可以做樣野－－投訴港鐵","createTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:47.000Z","uid":119550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6781b95023a4107ed521b4203a172074a10ecf5","tid":1453317,"uid":119550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"機場有冷氣有wifi，叫口號叫到無咩氣可以做啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然係問下我地親愛嘅港鐵點樣可以保障到市民安全啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信大家對於琴日葵芳站內發射催淚彈而今朝啲味仲末散呢件事記憶猶新。<br />\n<br />\n投訴熱線：<a href=\"http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Fcontact_us.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpCMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=043b9faa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/contact_us.html</a><br />\n用「提交網上意見」呢個function打埋問題俾佢地就ok的了。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要問啲咩？</span><br />\n作為一個返工無咩選擇只能搭港鐵的打工仔當然要關心當個問題：<br />\n1. 葵芳站有無毒氣殘留（如有，港鐵點解開放俾市民使用。如無，港鐵有咩理據話無）<br />\n2. 毒氣會唔會經通風系統流去其他站<br />\n3. 港鐵會唔會向警方追究係站內發射催淚彈嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n歡迎集思廣益，唔夠瞓諗唔到太多野。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"color: gold;\">1點機場見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}